Client null sending DISCONNECT

mosquitto_pub -h dev13.local -p 8883 -d --cafile /mosquitto/certs/ca.pem -u USER99 -P ed4139da17aacacac18c6cd10b7e7b8024e9c892 --tls-version tlsv1.3 -t hello/world -m "test"
